/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-youtube text-red-500 group-focus-within:scale-110 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.5 17a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0-10 2 2 0 0 1 1.4-1.4 49.56 49.56 0 0 1 16.2 0A2 2 0 0 1 21.5 7a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0 10 2 2 0 0 1-1.4 1.4 49.55 49.55 0 0 1-16.2 0A2 2 0 0 1 2.5 17\"></path><path d=\"m10 15 5-3-5-3z\"></path></svg></div><input class=\"\n              block w-full rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border text-white placeholder-zinc-700 \n              focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white/10 focus:bg-white/[0.05] transition-all duration-300\n              pl-12\n              pr-4\n              border-white/[0.08] hover:border-white/[0.15]\n              py-3 text-[14px] font-medium\n              h-14\n            \" placeholder=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=...\" value=\"\"/></div></div></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold rounded-xl transition-all active:scale-[0.98] disabled:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none gap-2.5 cursor-pointer no-underline tracking-tight bg-white text-black hover:bg-[#e2e2e2] shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] text-[15px] px-8 py-3.5 h-14 rounded-xl px-10\" disabled=\"\">Fetch Pipeline</button></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 pt-8 opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><div class=\"space-y-4 p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/[0.06] hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg><h4 class=\"text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-tighter\">Instant Bypass</h4><p class=\"text-[13px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed font-medium\">Direct connection to Google media servers ensures zero-bottleneck download speeds.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4 p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/[0.06] hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-music text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 18V5l12-2v13\"></path><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"18\" r=\"3\"></circle><circle cx=\"18\" cy=\"16\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg><h4 class=\"text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-tighter\">Studio Audio</h4><p class=\"text-[13px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed font-medium\">Extract high-bitrate M4A or WAV streams for professional audio production.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4 p-8 rounded-[2rem] bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/[0.06] hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock text-accent\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg><h4 class=\"text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-tighter\">Privacy Layer</h4><p class=\"text-[13px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed font-medium\">We proxy only the metadata. All file transfers are anonymous and unlogged.</p></div></div></div><!--/$--></div><footer class=\"mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 opacity-40 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h4 class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-accent tracking-[0.2em]\">Privacy</h4><p class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed\">Processing happens strictly on your machine. No data is ever transmitted or stored.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h4 class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-white tracking-[0.2em]\">Open Source</h4><p class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed\">Verified by the community. Part of the WokSpec Global Open Source Protocol.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h4 class=\"text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-white tracking-[0.2em]\">Performance</h4><p class=\"text-[11px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed\">Optimized for sub-millisecond response times using browser-native APIs.</p></div></footer></div></div><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-2d85b733eeeece9f.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0]);self.__next_f.push([2,null])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/bb3ef058b751a6ad-s.p.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n2:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/e4af272ccee01ff0-s.p.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n3:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/2060cbbad27f1202.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n4:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/42d10d262afb2c3a.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"5:I[11815,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n7:I[88311,[\\\"6340\\\",\\\"static/chunks/6340-faf5e4ae62415eb9.js\\\",\\\"9334\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/tools/yt-downloader/page-566bd025962508f7.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\n9:I[94112,[\\\"6340\\\",\\\"static/chunks/6340-faf5e4ae62415eb9.js\\\",\\\"9334\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/tools/yt-downloader/page-566bd025962508f7.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\na:I[55092,[],\\\"\\\"]\\nb:I[82023,[],\\\"\\\"]\\nc:I[12297,[\\\"7117\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/tools/error-a858148839906f4a.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\